<h1 class="govuk-heading-l datagovuk-heading-l">Births</h1>

<p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">This data includes annual live births, stillbirths, maternities and fertility rates in England and Wales up to 2024. Explore the data by factors including parent age, parent country of birth, ethnicity, deprivation, gestational age and birthweight. This dataset is owned by the Office for National Statistics (ONS).</p>



